---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="Celebrating 5 Years of parcelLab! - parcelLab"
  description="From three founders to 80+ team members across four offices, here's the story of parcelLab's first five years."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Company News</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">Celebrating 5 Years of parcelLab!</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab Team</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2020-08-28">August 28, 2020</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>4 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Body -->
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">How It All Started</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Tobias Buxhoidt and Julian Krenge connected through a matchmaking event at EU funding program "SpeedUp Europe." Anton Eder joined as the third founder through a job advertisement on the startup scene.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Through their logistics experience, the three recognized in 2014 that changes were needed in how retailers treated customers. The concept for parcelLab emerged from discussions with retailers who complained about lacking transparency and customer experience during shipping.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Our History</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The company grew from three founders to over 80 operations experience experts across four offices in Munich, London, Paris, and Los Angeles.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-28 text-sm font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Aug 2014</span>
            <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab idea founded</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-28 text-sm font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Jul 2015</span>
            <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">First customers test the solution</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-28 text-sm font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Sep 2016</span>
            <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Initial investors brought on board</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-28 text-sm font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Nov 2016</span>
            <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">More than 100 online shops live</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-28 text-sm font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Jan 2017</span>
            <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Moved to Munich Central Station office</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-28 text-sm font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Jun 2017</span>
            <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Over 250 online shops operational</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-28 text-sm font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Dec 2017</span>
            <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Series A financing secured</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-28 text-sm font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">May 2018</span>
            <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Relocated to Schillerstrasse office</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-28 text-sm font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Jul 2018</span>
            <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">UK market entry</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-28 text-sm font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Nov 2018</span>
            <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">London office opened</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-28 text-sm font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Oct 2019</span>
            <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Series B financing completed</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-28 text-sm font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Feb 2020</span>
            <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Paris office opened</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-28 text-sm font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Apr 2020</span>
            <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Los Angeles office opened</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-28 text-sm font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Jul 2020</span>
            <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">5th anniversary celebration</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Key Facts and Figures</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#3D3AD3]">80</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Employees</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#3D3AD3]">4</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Offices</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#3D3AD3]">500+</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Brands</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#3D3AD3]">45</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Countries</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Customer Quote</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"The GRANIT PARTS brand stands for customer orientation and reliability. This is evident in our shipping communication thanks to parcelLab."</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- Benjamin Luyten, Head of International Partner Shops at Granit Parts</p>
        </div>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Many thanks to our customers for their trust and loyalty over the past 5 years! parcelLab optimizes operations experience for over 500 brands to enhance customer shopping experiences.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
